{
  "stem": "15768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At any rate, to come back to the farm issue, we were always aware that we needed to be careful-- keep out of sight, not-- not be identified, and that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And one morning, early in the morning, I came in from my pasture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all the women were standing in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were very-- seemed very nervous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My mother looked particularly pale.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I came into the room, I realized there were two German soldiers standing in the kitchen, questioning them and not getting very far because they were speaking German.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And finally, in, exasperation, somebody said in French, anybody understand me, or whatever?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my little farmer's friend, farmer's daughter, my little friend, spoke up and pointed to me and said, she speaks German, at which point I think everybody turned very pale.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the soldier said, is that true?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you speak German?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, I had no choice but to admit that I did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the project for the day and the problem for the day was that they were looking for carrier pigeons which had gotten lost.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They assumed they were in some farmer's loft, mixed in with other pigeons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was their job to find these pigeons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after looking through the loft at our farmer's farm, they said, well, they were going to take me along and have me do the interpreting for the day or however long it was going to take to find the pigeons, at which point my mother's knees buckled.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And off I went at the age of 12 with-- not quite 12, but almost 12-- with these two German soldiers on a motorbike, a motorcycle with a sidecar.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went looking for pigeons.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
